#: (from de)
msgid "Length (2–25) of token sequences to compare; 25 should work well for at least moderately clean OCR. For very poor OCR, lower to 3 or 4."
msgstr "代币序列的长度(2-25)；25应至少适度清洁的OCR效果很好。对于非常差的OCR，较低至3或4。"

#: (from de)
msgid "Max offset"
msgstr "最大偏移"

#: (from de)
msgid "Enables max-offset and disables beam search. Maximum number of characters (20–80) difference between the aligned witness text and the original transcription."
msgstr "启用最大偏移量并禁用光束搜索。对齐的证人文本和原始转录之间的最大字符数(20-80)差异。"

#: (from de)
msgid "Beam size"
msgstr "梁尺寸"

#: (from de)
msgid "Enables beam search; if this and max offset are left unset, beam search will be on and beam size set to 20. Higher beam size (1-100) will result in slower computation but more accurate results."
msgstr "启用光束搜索；如果将其和最大偏移保持不设定，则梁搜索将打开，并且光束尺寸设置为20。较高的光束尺寸(1-100)将导致计算较慢，但结果更准确。"

#: (from de)
msgid "Gap"
msgstr "差距"

#: (from de)
msgid "The distance between matching unique n-grams; 600 should work well for clean OCR or texts where passages align to different portions of the witness text. To force end-to-end alignment of two documents, increase to 1,000,000."
msgstr "匹配唯一的n-gram之间的距离；600应该适合清洁的OCR或文本与证人文本的不同部分保持一致的文本。要强制两个文件的端到端对齐，请增加到1,000,000。"

